url=yes }}</ref>新聞行政人員協會則要求確保記者採訪不會受到無理及不必要限制。另外，亦有20多個網媒發表聲明，認為這是落後愚昧的舉動。<ref>{{cite news | url=https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=406546 | title=廿多個網媒批警方拒諸門外做法落後及愚昩 | publisher=[[now新聞|now新聞]] | date=2020-09-23 | access-date=2020-09-24 | archive-date=2021-01-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125004557/https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=406546 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

